Package: anomanor
Title: Anorectal Manometry Inter-Rater Agreement
Version: 1.6.3
Date/Publication: 28.05.2025
Author: Dieter Menne
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dieter", "Menne", email="dieter.menne@menne-biomed.de",
